{"tid":56754,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰維斯將投上海申花","createTime":"2016-12-27T13:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T14:37:27.000Z","uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b590973e9e7e83c1f192c0dc8ffd495b6a4c7430","tid":56754,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.performgroup.com/di/library/goal_de/41/b1/carlos-tevez-12112016_1q89fat3cmclrzyznd4nyf12w.jpg?t=577361456&amp;w=620&amp;h=430\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2Fgoal_de%2F41%2Fb1%2Fcarlos-tevez-12112016_1q89fat3cmclrzyznd4nyf12w.jpg%3Ft%3D577361456%26w%3D620%26h%3D430&h=53f971cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海申花教練普耶表示只欠一些細節，就會完成泰維斯的轉會。<br />\n<br />\n據報32歲的泰維斯已差不多完成由小保加轉投上海申花的手續，很快就會正式宣布轉會。<br />\n<br />\n申花教練普耶表示想公平對待今次轉會，以正等待球會百份百證實，才會正式宣佈。<br />\n<br />\n上海申花上季以第4名完成中超，比冠軍恒大少16分。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=PkCvH6rt5OWO8IJPVKTzOAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2fe51a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"af3063639d5c628e412687c18b1f9b1fff6a18a2","tid":56754,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:14:00.000Z","msg":"條友唔係有思鄉病先返阿根廷咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3211004dd7659fda419a3bd84e2b2d9c6b1c12","tid":56754,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友唔係有思鄉病先返阿根廷咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n$$$"},{"pid":"27c8032896758e1a31f39b72a0579ac22f634199","tid":56754,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"應該屈到機"},{"pid":"3eca0fae8c4ec36be5194a039886bdacf2cb9338","tid":56754,"uid":64699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:21:43.000Z","msg